  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel can be booked on a Room Only basis and does not have kitchen facilities for guests to cook in. Pangea’s on-site café/bar, The Living Room, has been designed as a welcoming space for guests to relax without needing to purchase anything.</p>
<p>The Living Room does have a great selection of food and drink, with everything from barista-made coffee and gourmet brunch items to artisan flatbread pizzas, craft beers and hand-crafted cocktails.</p>
<p>And if you’re looking for something different, Pangea is located right on the Village Stroll with a tonne of great restaurants, cafés and bars within easy walking distance.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
