<p><strong>Security</strong></p>
<p>Your suite is accessed via wristband keycards, with access limited to only those guests staying in that particular suite. Suites are male and female mixed dorms.</p>
<p>Locks are not provided, and are available for purchase at reception.</p>
<p>Valuables – Each pod has its own lockable cubby.</p>
<p>Luggage – Each pod contains an area where you can secure your suitcase using a security cable.</p>
<p>Ski storage – Every guest is provided with a rack for skis/snowboards and a locker for accessories (boots, helmets, goggles, etc.) in The Toy Box, Pangea’s secure gear storage area.</p>]]></facilityDescription>
