  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>Each pod has its own secluded double bed and privacy curtain. Pods are arranged in suites, which contain Pangea’s innovative bathroom ‘components’ including shower cabins, bathrooms, changing rooms and stand-alone vanities.</p>
<p>Each pod can accommodate up to two guests, though we only recommend sharing for couples. If you’re travelling with friends, having your own private pod will ensure the best experience.</p>
<p><strong>Pod Facilities</strong></p>
